"register user sessions, it is a good idea to build <application>Polkit</"
"application> with PAM support so <phrase revision=\"sysv\"><command>elogind</"
"command></phrase> <phrase revision=\"systemd\"><command>systemd-logind</"
"command></phrase> can track <application>Polkit</application> sessions."
